<p>In the January issue of the <italic>Journal of Biomolecular Screening</italic>, in the above-mentioned editorial, the following sentence should have the date “1996” instead of “1999.” The corrected sentence is below.</p>
<p>Since its inception in 1996, JBS manuscript submissions have increased more than fivefold, from approximately 40 to over 200 in 2011 (from over 30 countries!).</p>
